{"type": "article", "id": 24005, "title": "黑色丝线灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-17T07:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104633t3JhGbCO0TAQZH8v.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款灯来自日本建筑师伊东丰雄，他在玻璃罩上用了黑色的丝线制作，横竖丝线在上面细密地铺开，在灯光的照射下可以看到明显的明暗差别，倒有点像素描画中的球体。尽管使用了轻盈的材料，却表现出了厚重感，可以应用在多个场合中。<a href=\"http://en.yamagiwa.co.jp/series/detail/1/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104629zy8Skfevo5PlRc3w.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071046305EsW47o0eIh3C2HV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31295844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104631Pbxfe5JG8ZBdpFwN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060710463297QfF6rCH0OmkpgP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.97465146\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}